 “性教育”和“Heartstopper”亲密协调员回应对该角色的批评https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sex-education-heartstopper-intimacy-coordinator-responds-criticisms-of-role-3503317?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sex-education-heartstopper-intimacy-coordinator-回应对角色的批评Hollie GeraghtySun, 24 Sep 2023 17:53:10 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3503317 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “了解它的内容，希望您有一个愉快的过程”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sex-education-heartstopper-intimacy-coordinator-responds-criticisms-of-role-3503317">《性教育》和《Heartstopper》亲密协调员的帖子回应了对该角色的批评，该角色</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Sex-Education-S4-2-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sex-education"><em>《性教育》</em></a>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/heartstopper" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《心跳停止》</a></em>背后的亲密协调员回应了有关他们在电影和电视剧中扮演的角色的批评。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/sex-education-season-4-review-3501183">《性教育》第四季评论：饥渴的高中生一起出去玩</a></strong></li></ul><p>亲密协调员与导演、演员和工作人员合作，帮助规划亲密场景并确保演员的健康。</p><p>近年来，关于亲密协调员所扮演的角色的讨论变得越来越普遍。今年夏天，艾丹·特纳<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/aidan-turner-criticises-lack-of-intimacy-coordinators-on-past-projects-3469365">批评他参与的过去项目中缺乏亲密协调员</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kate-winslet-intimacy-coordinators-helped-awkward-sex-scenes-2879617">凯特·温斯莱特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-says-she-could-have-benefitted-from-intimacy-coordinators-as-a-young-actor-2710629">莎朗·斯通</a>等演员也表示，他们本来可以从之前项目的片场中受益。</p><p>然而，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sean-bean-says-intimacy-coordinators-spoil-sex-scenes-3286373">肖恩·宾去年表示，他们“破坏了性爱场面的自发性”</a> ，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sean-bean-criticised-by-hollywood-actresses-for-comments-on-intimacy-coordinators-3287328">后来他遭到了几位女演员的批评</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-caine">迈克尔·凯恩</a>还在一次新的采访中质疑了他们的必要性。 “在我那个时代，你只是拍了爱情场景，然后就没有人干涉，”他告诉<em><a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-12540335/We-never-intimacy-coordinators-day-MICHAEL-CAINE-calls-woke-dull-says-young-man-national-service-truly-makes-man-reflects-acting-90.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《每日邮报》</a></em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3499930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3499930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3499930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield.jpg" alt="性教育第四季" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3499930" class="wp-caption-text">阿萨·巴特菲尔德在《性教育》第四季中。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>现在，<em>性教育的</em>亲密关系首席协调员大卫·萨克雷在接受<em><a href="https://www.radiotimes.com/tv/comedy/sex-education-intimacy-coordinator-criticism-response-exclusive-newsupdate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《广播时报》</a></em>的新采访时分享了他对此事的看法，他在谈到这些批评时表示：“我完全明白他们的来源。”</p><p> “这是很典型的事情，因为当我接受亲密协调员培训时，在它建立之前，我担心‘这真的只是为了一点健康和安全吗？它会妨碍表演或导演吗？它会妨碍进程吗？</p><p> “但是一旦你经历了这一切，一旦你真正与亲密协调员合作，并经历了一个出色的过程，你就可以说，‘哦，我发现了更多细节。我仍然可以尊重你的表演过程，我仍然尊重你的导演过程，我只是会给你一些工具，让你能够‘哦，这容易多了，我们就这么做’ ”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473188" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473188" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473188" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix.jpg" alt="心塞" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Heartstopper_Season_2_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473188" class="wp-caption-text">乔·洛克和基特·康纳在《Heartstopper》第二季中回归。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>萨克雷继续说道：“或者，‘哇，有了这种开放的沟通和同意，我们可以走得更远’。”当你有一个亲密协调员并且你们已经进行了对话和沟通时，我就不必以我真正担心的方式考虑我的场景伙伴。</p><p>他总结道：“所以对我来说，我认为，找出它的含义，希望你能与一位出色的亲密协调员一起度过一个愉快的过程，并希望你会改变主意。”</p><p>萨克雷还担任过<em>《我恨苏西》</em> 、 <em>《白莲花》</em>第二季、 <em>《工业》</em>和<em>《这是罪孽》</em>的亲密关系协调员。</p><p>另一方面， <em>《性爱自修室》</em>主创<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sex-education-creator-laurie-nunn-opens-up-about-cast-departures-3502943">劳里·纳恩 (Laurie Nunn) 公开了该剧最后一季在 Netflix 播出后演员阵容的退出情况</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sex-education-heartstopper-intimacy-coordinator-responds-criticisms-of-role-3503317">《性教育》和《Heartstopper》亲密协调员的帖子回应了对该角色的批评，该角色</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
